\c 7
\s Kuzvidavirira kwaSitefano
\p
\v 1 Zvino mupristi mukuru akati: Ko zvinhu izvi zvakadai here?
\v 2 Zvino akati: Varume, hama nemadzibaba, teererai. Mwari wekubwinya wakaonekwa kuna baba vedu Abhurahama vari muMesopotamia, vasati vagara Harani,
\v 3 akati kwaari: Buda munyika yako nekuhama dzako, uuye kunyika yandichakuratidza.
\v 4 Zvino vakabuda munyika yeVaKaradhia, vakagara muHarani; zvino kubva ipapo shure kwekufa kwababa vavo, wakavabvisira kunyika iyi yamunogara imwi ikozvino;
\v 5 asi haana kuvapa nhaka mairi, kwete kunyange chitsiko chetsoka, asi wakavimbisa kuvapa iyo ive yavo, neyembeu yavo shure kwavo, vasati vava nemwana.
\v 6 Mwari ndokutaura seizvi, kuti mbeu yavo ichava mutorwa kunyika yeumweni, uye vachaiita nhapwa neku\add i\add*bata zvakaipa makore mazana mana;
\v 7 asi rudzi urwo rwavachava varanda kwarwuri ndicharwutonga ini, wakadaro Mwari; uye shure kweizvozvo vachabuda vagondishumira panzvimbo ino.
\v 8 Zvino akavapa sungano yedzingiso, naizvozvowo vakabereka Isaka, vakamudzingisa zuva rerusere; naIsaka \add wakabereka\add* Jakobho; naJakobho mateteguru gumi nemaviri.
\v 9 Mateteguru akagodoka, vakatengesa Josefa kuEgipita; asi Mwari waiva naye.
\v 10 Akamusunungura pamatambudziko ake ese, akamupa nyasha nenjere pamberi paFarao mambo weEgipita; ndokumuita mutungamiriri pamusoro peEgipita neimba yake yose.
\v 11 Zvino kwakauya nzara panyika yose yeEgipita neKenani, nedambudziko guru; madzibaba edu akasawana kudya.
\v 12 Asi Jakobho wakati anzwa kuti kwaiva nezviyo kuEgipita, wakatuma madzibaba edu kwekutanga.
\v 13 Zvino kwechipiri Josefa wakaziviswa kuvanakomana vababa vake; uye rudzi rwaJosefa rwukaziviswa kuna Farao.
\v 14 Zvino Josefa akatumira akadana baba vake Jakobho nehama dzake dzose, iri mweya makumi manomwe nemishanu.
\v 15 Zvino Jakobho akaburukira Egipita, ndokufa iye nemadzibaba edu;
\v 16 uye vakatakurirwa Shekemi, vakaradzikwa paguva Abhurahama raaiva atenga nemutengo wesirivha kuvanakomana vaEmori weShekemi.
\v 17 Zvino nguva yechivimbiso yakati yaswedera Mwari chaaiva apikira kuna Abhurahama, vanhu vakakura, vakawanda muEgipita,
\v 18 kusvika umwe mambo amuka waiva asingazivi Josefa.
\v 19 Ndiye wakabata rudzi rwedu nemano-mano, akatambudza madzibaba edu, achivarasisa vacheche vavo kuti varege kurarama.
\v 20 Munguva iyoyo Mozisi wakaberekwa, uye waiva akanaka kuna Mwari; ndokurerwa mumba mababa vake mwedzi mitatu.
\v 21 Zvino wakati araswa, mukunda waFarao akamunonga, akazvirerera iye kuti ave mwanakomana \add wake\add*.
\v 22 Mozisi akadzidziswa muuchenjeri hwese hweVaEgipita; akava nesimba pamashoko nepamabasa.
\v 23 Zvino makore makumi mana akati asvika kwaari, zvakasvika mumoyo make kushanyira hama dzake, vana vaIsraeri.
\v 24 Zvino achiona umwe achiitirwa zvisakarurama, aka\add mu\add*rwira ndokutsivira waiva achitambudzwa, akarova muEgipita;
\v 25 zvino waifunga kuti hama dzake dzichanzwisisa kuti Mwari anovapa ruponeso neruoko rwake; asi havana kunzwisisa.
\v 26 Zvino zuva raitevera wakazvionesa kwavari vachirwa, akavayananisa nesimba achiti: Varume, imwi muri hama; munoitiranirei zvisakarurama?
\v 27 Zvino iye waiva achiitira umwe wake zvakaipa wakamusundidzira achiti: Ndiani wakuita mutungamiriri nemutongi pamusoro pedu?
\v 28 Iwe unoda kundiuraya, sezvo wakauraya muEgipita zuro here?
\v 29 Zvino neshoko iri Mozisi wakatiza, ndokuva mutorwa munyika yeMidhiani, kwaakabereka vanakomana vaviri.
\v 30 Zvino makore makumi mana akati azadziswa, kwakaonekwa kwaari murenje regomo Sinai mutumwa waIshe mumurazvo wemoto we\add mu\add*gwenzi.
\v 31 Mozisi wakati aona, akashamisika nechionekwa ichi; zvino paaiswedera kunocherekedza, inzwi raIshe rikasvika kwaari \add richiti\add*:
\v 32 Ndini Mwari wemadzibaba ako, Mwari waAbhurahama, naMwari waIsaka, naMwari waJakobho. Zvino Mozisi akadedera akasashinga kucherekedza.
\v 33 Zvino Ishe akati kwaari: Kurura shangu patsoka dzako, nokuti nzvimbo yaumire pairi ivhu dzvene.
\v 34 Ndaonesesa dambudziko revanhu vangu vari muEgipita, ndikanzwa kugomera kwavo, zvino ndaburuka kuzovasunungura; ikozvino uya, ndichakutuma kuEgipita.
\v 35 Uyu Mozisi wavakaramba vachiti: Ndiani wakakuita mutungamiri nemutongi? Ndiye Mwari waakatuma \add kuva \add*mutungamiriri nemudzukunuri neruoko rwemutumwa, wakaonekwa kwaari mugwenzi.
\v 36 Iye akavabudisa, aita zvishamiso nezviratidzo munyika yeEgipita nemuGungwa Dzvuku, nemurenje makore makumi mana.
\v 37 Ndiye uyu Mozisi wakati kuvana vaIsraeri: Ishe Mwari wenyu achakumutsirai Muporofita pahama dzenyu, wakafanana neni; muchamunzwa iye.
\v 38 Uyu ndiye waiva ari mukereke murenje, ane mutumwa wakataura naye mugomo Sinai ane madzibaba edu; wakagamuchira mashoko mapenyu kuti atipe.
\v 39 Ndiye madzibaba edu wavaiva vasingadi kuteerera; asi vaka\add mu\add*sundidzira parutivi, vakadzokera kuEgipita mumoyo yavo.
\v 40 Vachiti kuna Aroni: Tiitire vamwari vachatitungamirira; nokuti Mozisi uyu wakatibudisa munyika yeEgipita, hatizivi zvamuwira.
\v 41 Zvino vakaita mhuru mumazuva ayo, vakauisa chibairo kuchifananidzo, vakafara nemabasa emaoko avo.
\v 42 Zvino Mwari akafuratira, akavakumikidza kuti vashumire hondo yekudenga, sezvakanyorwa mubhuku revaporofita, \add zvichinzi\add*: Ko makauisa kwandiri here zvibairo nezvipo makore makumi mana murenje, imwi imba yaIsraeri?
\v 43 Uye makatakura tabhenakeri yaMoroki, nenyeredzi yamwari wenyu Remifani, zvifananidzo zvamakaita kuti muzvinamate; uye ndichakutamisirai mberi kweBhabhironi.
\v 44 Madzibaba edu aiva netabhenakeri yeuchapupu murenje, sekuraira kwaiye wakataura naMozisi kuti aiite nemufananidzo waaiva aona;
\v 45 yakatiwo madzibaba edu aitevera aigamuchira, akaipinza pamwe naJoshua munhumbi dzevahedheni, Mwari vaakadzinga pamberi pechiso chemadzibaba edu, kusvika kumazuva aDhavhidhi;
\v 46 wakawana nyasha pamberi paMwari, akakumbira kuwanira Mwari waJakobho tabhenakeri.
\v 47 Asi Soromoni wakamuvakira imba.
\v 48 Asi Wekumusoro-soro haagari mutembere dzakaitwa nemaoko, sezvinoreva muporofita \add achiti\add*:
\v 49 Denga chigaro changu cheushe, nenyika chitsiko chetsoka dzangu; muchandivakira imba yakadini? \add ndizvo\add* zvinoreva Ishe; kana nzvimbo yezororo rangu ndeipi?
\v 50 Ruoko rwangu haruna kuita zvinhu izvi zvese here?
\v 51 Imwi vemitsipa mikukutu uye vasina kudzingiswa pamoyo nenzeve, imwi munogara muchipikisa Mweya Mutsvene; semadzibaba enyu saizvozvo imwi.
\v 52 Ndeupi wevaporofita madzibaba enyu wavasina kushusha? Vakauraya avo vaifanozivisa nezvekuuya kweWakarurama, iye ikozvino wamava vatengesi nevaurayi vake.
\v 53 Imwi vakagamuchira murairo neurongwa hwevatumwa, asi mukasa\add u\add*chengeta.
\p
\v 54 Zvino vanzwa zvinhu izvi vakabaiwa pamoyo yavo, vakamugedera-gedera meno.
\v 55 Asi azere neMweya Mutsvene wakatarisisa kudenga, akaona kubwinya kwaMwari, naJesu amire kuruoko rwerudyi rwaMwari,
\v 56 akati: Tarirai, ndinoona matenga akazaruka, neMwanakomana wemunhu amire kuruoko rwerudyi rwaMwari.
\v 57 Zvino vakadanidzira nenzwi guru, vakadzivira nzeve dzavo, vakamhanyira paari nemoyo umwe;
\v 58 vaka\add mu\add*budisira kunze kweguta, ndoku\add mu\add*taka nemabwe; nezvapupu zvikaisa nguvo dzazvo patsoka dzejaya rainzi Sauro.
\v 59 Zvino vakataka Sitefano nemabwe, achidana achiti: Ishe Jesu, gamuchirai mweya wangu.
\v 60 Zvino wakafugama, akadanidzira nenzwi guru, \add achiti\add*: Ishe, musavaverengera chivi ichi. Zvino wakati areva izvi, akarara.